<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Blog Tutorials 📚</h2>
          <p class="lead text-center">
            Learn how to use <strong>Blog'sTer</strong> step by step.  
            Whether you’re new or experienced, these tutorials will help you get started.
          </p>

          <div class="accordion mt-4" id="tutorialAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
                  1️⃣ Signing Up & Logging In
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#tutorialAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Click on <strong>Sign Up</strong> in the navbar.<br>
                  - Enter your email and password.<br>
                  - After registering, log in to start posting!
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
                  2️⃣ Creating Your First Post
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#tutorialAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Navigate to <strong>New Post</strong>.<br>
                  - Add a title and body content.<br>
                  - Click <strong>Create Post</strong> and it will appear on your profile.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
                  3️⃣ Viewing & Managing Posts
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#tutorialAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Go to your <strong>Profile</strong> to view all your posts.<br>
                  - Edit or delete posts whenever you need.<br>
                  - Posts are visible to all logged-in users.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-4 text-center">
            🚀 Keep exploring, writing, and sharing your thoughts with the world!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
